# Feature 17 - Authentication & Cloud Synchronization

## Objective

Implement a secure Authentication and Cloud Synchronization module that enables users to create accounts, securely log in, synchronize their health data across devices, and protect sensitive medical information.

This feature establishes secure user identity management and cloud storage for prediction history, user profiles, and application preferences.

